Class Cubin

java.lang.Object
  org.lambdacomplex.nn.javacuda.Cubin

public class Cubin
extends java.lang.Object

This class encapsulates modules in their source and compiled forms. The compiled data exists as a temporary file on the hard drive of the computer.
